{"tid":1382030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[運動正名] 不如我地叫呢塲運動做「光復香港」","createTime":"2019-07-29T11:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T17:41:50.000Z","uid":81424,"like":197,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"f649ee219168200a32448d9f6c3f291f50b886de","tid":1382030,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:19:32.000Z","msg":"呢塲運動由最開始反對逃犯條例修訂呢個單一議題嘅100萬人大遊行<br />\n已經演變為五大訴求缺一不可嘅一塲運動<br />\n「反送中」呢三隻字漸漸已經唔能夠槪括呢塲運動<br />\n我地必須搵新名去命名呢塲革命<br />\n<br />\n有外國傳媒叫呢塲革命做「安全帽革命」（傳送門：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1381803/page/1）\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1381803/page/1）</a><br />\n但由於太膠嘅關係 小弟建議另擇新名<br />\n<br />\n鑑於大家次次遊行都叫「光復香港 時代革命」（亦都係本民前嘅選舉口號）<br />\n小弟愚見不如正名今次革命為「<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>光復香港</strong></span>」<br />\n英文為「<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Liberation of Hong Kong</strong></span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 <br />\n時代革命<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong  <br />\nThe revolution of our times</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"46e3f2cab18666603c20a6fb953bcf86bf107a04","tid":1382030,"uid":81424,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:19:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">85全港大罷工</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"082b86272063788706bc94e707661a9f8ea21185","tid":1382030,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:20:09.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［長文慎屌］727 728 賽後檢討<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380074</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"22188a6b927a81d8ea92006a09b592a5f661971f","tid":1382030,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:20:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d37c1c2c11cfb7d85b65a6a24b9400f388f8bb6","tid":1382030,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:20:41.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令黑警有所顧忌有所恐懼！ 如何從狗屋內部分解黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378251</a>"},{"pid":"fc391af868b04ae687ae3938da323003720ade3e","tid":1382030,"uid":81424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:22:03.000Z","msg":"五大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選"},{"pid":"17e008e6e5531b0157e96f3f80bb2f6cdd6fbabd","tid":1382030,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a896ecf997a2c67d04b545d17ab66285e588d446","tid":1382030,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985d173e655b9da3939fc07cfce9996b2d009673","tid":1382030,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:29:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1478522832427be682d4dd3f377ee0245cbbf78","tid":1382030,"uid":184366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:30:43.000Z","msg":"贊成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d653777cb43b9c15ddfe3962d1d327b089f82d4b","tid":1382030,"ui