moji\" />"},{"pid":"08cd91e7d3440b787a464fc2789ce1251d3306b9","tid":1382030,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f649ee219168200a32448d9f6c3f291f50b886de","tid":1382030,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:19:32.000Z","msg":"呢塲運動由最開始反對逃犯條例修訂呢個單一議題嘅100萬人大遊行<br />\n已經演變為五大訴求缺一不可嘅一塲運動<br />\n「反送中」呢三隻字漸漸已經唔能夠槪括呢塲運動<br />\n我地必須搵新名去命名呢塲革命<br />\n<br />\n有外國傳媒叫呢塲革命做「安全帽革命」（傳送門：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1381803/page/1）\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1381803/page/1）</a><br />\n但由於太膠嘅關係 小弟建議另擇新名<br />\n<br />\n鑑於大家次次遊行都叫「光復香港 時代革命」（亦都係本民前嘅選舉口號）<br />\n小弟愚見不如正名今次革命為「<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>光復香港</strong></span>」<br />\n英文為「<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Liberation of Hong Kong</strong></span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 <br />\n時代革命<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong  <br />\nThe revolution of our times</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:06:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12b4fa1b30cb91e127d275a5693eadd480f2164","tid":1382030,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946b3f225b829ff0c738e3bf38786765d848ef23","tid":1382030,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:17:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7ce428aa9df4ddc19ebed0f552be08d08e3106f5","tid":1382030,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:18:10.000Z","msg":"要話比多Ｄ人知，要做埋文宣圖，